        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", either by an error of the understanding, or by evil communications [conversation] or by corrupt manners. Those, who place sin in the will alone, and not in the understanding, are in error, and therefore commit sin. Arguments calculated to rouse are added to those used as proofs, as ",
